Roe vs. Wade. Hunter played McCorvey in a TV movie. ; Photo, Thousands turned 
out for a star-studded pro-choice rally at Rancho Park. The program featured a 
lineup of celebrities. PATRICK DOWNS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
