<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: LOS ALAMITOS; 
</P>
<P>
APPLICANTS SOUGHT FOR FINE ARTS PANEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The City Council is seeking applications from residents interested in serving 
on the Fine Arts and Cultural Affairs Commission. 
</P>
<P>
The seven-member commission meets the third Wednesday of every month at 7 p.m. 
in the council chambers and plans annual events that promote the fine arts. 
</P>
<P>
Applicants should send letters to the City Clerk, P.O. Box 3147, Los Alamitos, 
Calif. 90720. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
