BOSTER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Running back Brian Pizula is one of the 
reasons Sunny Hills has a 10-0 record and is top seeded in Division VI. STEVE 
TOWNSLEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
