<P>
West Virginia University will play in the Gator Bowl in Jacksonville, Fla., on 
Dec. 30, with Clemson as the Mountaineers' likely opponent, a newspaper 
reported today. 
</P>
<P>
The Times-West Virginian of Fairmont, quoting "reliable sources," said WVU 
